# plant-pollinator-mpl-062

## Summary

This is a hypergraph dataset where nodes are plants species, and hyperedges are pollinator species that visit a given plant. 


Locality of study: Carlinville, Illinois, USA (latitude: 39.278958, longitude: -89.8968771).

## Statistics
Some basic statistics of this dataset are:
* number of nodes: 456
* number of hyperedges: 1,044
* distribution of the connected components:
<center>

| Component Size  | Number |
| ----- | ---- |
| 456 | 1 |
</center>

