## Source of original data
Source: [web-of-life](https://www.web-of-life.es/), dataset ID: M_PL_062.

## References
If you use this dataset, please cite these references:
* Robertson, C. 1929. "Flowers and insects: lists of visitors to four hundred and fifty-three flowers". Carlinville, IL, USA, C. Robertson.

